# =============================================================================
# QUICK SETUP GUIDE
# =============================================================================
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env.local
# 2. Create Supabase project: https://supabase.com/dashboard
# 3. Get Google Maps API key: https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 4. Generate session secret: openssl rand -base64 32
# 5. Choose AI provider and get API key
# 6. (Optional) Set up Airtable for content management
# 7. Run: npm run env:validate to check configuration
# 8. Start development: npm run dev

# =============================================================================
# VALIDATION COMMANDS
# =============================================================================
# Validate all required environment variables are set:
# npm run env:validate
#
# Interactive environment setup:
# npm run env:setup
#
# Check environment status:
# npm run env:check